citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:54pm on March
2nd, 2023. Inspectors rang doorbell at 5:54pm; no responsible adult available. Called (5:57pm) and texted (6:11pm)
contact number requesting a call back. No response received from registrant within 30 minutes.
Additional Inspectors:
SARA TOBIAS, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
